WEBVTT

00:00:01.632 --> 00:00:02.785
OKAY, THIS IS

00:00:02.785 --> 00:00:08.725
TAPE TWO OF AN INTERVIEW WITH Basye Soyfer. SEVENTEEN MAY, NINETEEN NINETY-EIGHT,

00:00:08.725 --> 00:00:10.266
IN BROOKLYN, NEW YORK.

00:00:12.516 --> 00:00:13.725
iz,

00:00:15.773 --> 00:00:17.724
vegn ayer kindershe lebn,

00:00:19.114 --> 00:00:23.580
 volt ir gezogt az geven, ir zayt geven tsufridn?

00:00:25.476 --> 00:00:27.292
s'iz geven a gliklekhe lebn?

00:00:27.282 --> 00:00:28.187
ven?

00:00:28.092 --> 00:00:29.902
 ven ir zayt geven a kind,

00:00:29.902 --> 00:00:31.004
farn krig.

00:00:30.387 --> 00:00:32.895
nu, far dem krig iz geven,

00:00:33.222 --> 00:00:34.431
a mitl lebn.

00:00:35.044 --> 00:00:39.054
m'hot, m'hot geredt a mol vegn forn keyn Yisroel?

00:00:40.326 --> 00:00:42.142
oyle zayn keyn Yisroel?

00:00:42.030 --> 00:00:47.036
nu, denstmol iz avekgeforn, a sakh mentshn flegn avekforn keyn Yisroel.

00:00:47.228 --> 00:00:52.048
yu- yunge khevre un meydlekh makhn ⟨HASHARA⟩, ⟨ikh veys vi azoy me zogt⟩, HAKHSHARA,

00:00:52.189 --> 00:00:55.418
forn atin keyn IZRAIL'. zenen geforn, he...

00:00:55.783 --> 00:01:00.249
m'hot ge-, az, es zaynen tsienistn, heyst es?

00:00:59.833 --> 00:01:00.738
yo.

00:01:01.234 --> 00:01:06.273
iz, di tsienistn hobn zikh tsekrigt mit, anti-tsienistn?

00:01:06.448 --> 00:01:07.842
s'iz geven,

00:01:08.355 --> 00:01:10.222
ikh, ikh d-...

00:01:08.592 --> 00:01:11.218
a krigeray vegn dem, ⟨tsi⟩, vos ir gedenkt?

00:01:11.005 --> 00:01:15.589
neyn, dos gedenk ikh nit. ikh veys, m'hot gezogt, s'iz avekgeforn mentshn keyn IZRAIL'.

00:01:16.354 --> 00:01:18.103
dos iz geven shoyn

00:01:19.915 --> 00:01:22.727
in draysik akht,

00:01:23.695 --> 00:01:25.545
draysik nayn, azoy shoyn.

00:01:26.023 --> 00:01:28.160
 tsi zaynen geven,

00:01:28.403 --> 00:01:30.371
khsidim in ayer shtot?

00:01:30.192 --> 00:01:31.316
s'iz geven.

00:01:31.879 --> 00:01:34.505
 ayer mishpokhe iz geven khsidish?

00:01:34.090 --> 00:01:36.446
 ⟨i-⟩ bay mir ⟨z- zenen⟩ gev-,

00:01:37.701 --> 00:01:38.640
neyn.

00:01:39.844 --> 00:01:42.504
tsi gedenkt ir tsi,

00:01:42.527 --> 00:01:46.267
khsidim hobn zikh tsekrigt mit, misnagdim,

00:01:46.425 --> 00:01:47.651
mit,...?

00:01:46.476 --> 00:01:48.051
neyn. neyn.

00:01:49.851 --> 00:01:56.443
 zayt ir geven gevoyer fun politishe parteyen, yidishe oder nit-yidishe?

00:01:55.504 --> 00:01:57.742
mir ze'mir nit geven in di parteyen.

00:01:59.470 --> 00:02:04.020
vos far a tsaytungen hot men geleyent demolt? s'iz geven a yidishe tsaytung?

00:02:02.305 --> 00:02:04.842
yidish. a yidishe tsaytung.

00:02:04.077 --> 00:02:05.927
ir gedenkt vi zi heyst?

00:02:05.173 --> 00:02:06.061
neyn.

00:02:06.658 --> 00:02:09.486
ayer tate fleg leyenen di tsaytungen?

00:02:08.059 --> 00:02:09.521
yidish, yo.

00:02:10.303 --> 00:02:13.334
 ir hot demolt geleyent, yidish?

00:02:13.746 --> 00:02:14.887
ikh, neyn.

00:02:17.020 --> 00:02:19.036
hebreish hot ir oykh...?

00:02:18.893 --> 00:02:22.346
neyn. mayn shvester ken; zi leyent un shraybt yidish.

00:02:19.348 --> 00:02:20.226
UNK

00:02:24.343 --> 00:02:25.720
iz,

00:02:27.988 --> 00:02:30.361
vos hot ir gehert fun

00:02:30.385 --> 00:02:32.525
di problemen arum aykh,

00:02:32.525 --> 00:02:34.733
in Rusland oder in Daytshland,

00:02:35.413 --> 00:02:37.938
ven ir zayt geven a kind in di draysiker,

00:02:38.383 --> 00:02:42.916
mistome in di shpeterdike draysiker? hot ir gehert epes vegn Daytshland, tsum bayshpil?

00:02:43.648 --> 00:02:50.675
 neyn, fun Daytshland ⟨hob ikh⟩ nor gevust fun, in eyn un fertsikstn hob ikh nor gevust. vayter hobn mir nit gevust fun Daytshland gornit.

00:02:52.491 --> 00:02:54.884
iz, ven ir zayt geborn gevorn,

00:02:54.884 --> 00:02:58.070
ayer shtetl iz geven a teyl fun Rumenyen, yo?

00:02:58.380 --> 00:02:59.673
un

00:03:01.958 --> 00:03:10.862
tsi zaynen, hot men gehert fun komunizm? iz, iz komunizm geven shtark a, a, a bavegung in, in der, ⟨di⟩ gegnt demolt?

00:03:07.442 --> 00:03:08.448
neyn.

00:03:08.708 --> 00:03:09.951
NO. NO.

00:03:10.277 --> 00:03:11.098
neyn.

00:03:11.121 --> 00:03:13.410
denstmol ⟨hot men nokh⟩ nit gevust ⟨veg⟩n komunizm.

00:03:13.024 --> 00:03:14.024
⟨⟩.

00:03:14.361 --> 00:03:16.619
iz, hot ir gehert propagande

00:03:16.619 --> 00:03:19.788
vegn Daytshland oder vegn Rusland? kimat nit?

00:03:18.310 --> 00:03:19.131
NO.

00:03:22.090 --> 00:03:23.484
iz,

00:03:25.482 --> 00:03:30.842
kent ir dertseyln, vos hot pasirt in di shpeterdike draysiker yorn? vos hot,

00:03:31.590 --> 00:03:33.086
vos hot aykh pasirt,

00:03:33.328 --> 00:03:35.212
tsum bayshpil, nayn un draysik,

00:03:35.218 --> 00:03:37.625
ven di milkhome hot zikh oysgebrokhn?

00:03:37.902 --> 00:03:41.844
 neyn, di milkho- di milkhome iz nit geven in nayn un draysik.

00:03:38.020 --> 00:03:39.701
tsi hot ir gehert vegn dem?

00:03:42.593 --> 00:03:44.848
di milkhome iz geven in eyn un fertsikstn.

00:03:46.238 --> 00:03:48.240
yo, in Poyln iz geven

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:51.851
dos iz geven in Poyln. n⟨u⟩, dos,... yo.

00:03:48.786 --> 00:03:52.470
⟨bay⟩, bay zey a milkhome. ir hot gornisht gehert fun dem?

00:03:51.851 --> 00:03:52.593
neyn.

00:03:53.865 --> 00:03:55.370
iz,

00:03:55.370 --> 00:04:00.288
ay- ⟨iz, dos⟩ heyst az s'iz, ayer lebn iz geven in gantsn normal biz,

00:04:00.717 --> 00:04:02.567
 biz eyn un fertsik?

00:04:02.202 --> 00:04:03.039
yo.

00:04:03.096 --> 00:04:06.634
ven, di rusn zaynen gekumen...

00:04:07.011 --> 00:04:08.844
ven zaynen di rusn gekumen?

00:04:09.120 --> 00:04:11.999
 di rusn zenen gekumen bay undz in fertsikstn,

00:04:12.732 --> 00:04:17.046
un zenen geven a yor un nokh dem iz shoyn gekumen nokh a mol di,

00:04:17.980 --> 00:04:19.239
di daytshn.

00:04:19.144 --> 00:04:21.045
vos kent ir gedenken,

00:04:21.067 --> 00:04:24.032
ven di rusn zaynen gekumen? vos hot pasirt

00:04:24.375 --> 00:04:25.567
in ayer lebn?

00:04:27.582 --> 00:04:31.761
ven di rusn zenen gekumen, hobn zey gemakht fun di mentshn gornit.

00:04:31.885 --> 00:04:33.839
ver s'hot gehat zayn magazin,

00:04:33.839 --> 00:04:36.739
hobn zey tsugenemen; s'iz gevorn aldings bay der melukhe.

00:04:37.723 --> 00:04:39.117
dos gedenk ikh.

00:04:43.528 --> 00:04:50.103
iz, ayer lebn iz gebitn? ir zayt gegangen in naye shuln? tsi di shuln hobn zikh gebitn?

00:04:50.734 --> 00:04:51.335
neyn.

00:04:54.767 --> 00:04:57.495
hot ir gehert propagande far di rusn

00:04:58.294 --> 00:04:59.891
ven zey zenen arayn?

00:04:58.429 --> 00:04:59.570
mir hob'mir ⟨z-⟩

00:04:59.577 --> 00:05:05.511
denstmol hobn mir nokh nit farshtanen keyn rusish. mir hob'mir ge⟨hert redn⟩ mentshn; m'hot nokh nit farshtanen keyn rusish, ⟨azoy se darf tsu zayn⟩.

00:05:05.668 --> 00:05:08.210
m'hot nit uspeyet tsu lernen nokh keyn rusish.

00:05:11.203 --> 00:05:12.496
iz,

00:05:16.148 --> 00:05:22.099
tsi hobn ayere ki- ayere shvester o- oder brider oder tate-mame geredt vegn dem vos tut zikh?

00:05:23.607 --> 00:05:25.491
i- ⟨UNK⟩kh gedenk nit dos.

00:05:26.931 --> 00:05:27.903
iz,

00:05:27.903 --> 00:05:29.810
vos, gedenkt ir

00:05:29.918 --> 00:05:31.852
dernokh? vos hot pasirt

00:05:32.213 --> 00:05:35.042
ven di rusn zaynen gekumen un shpeter?

00:05:36.381 --> 00:05:39.480
 ven s'iz gekumen di rumeners UNK in eyn un fertsikstn?

00:05:44.110 --> 00:05:50.364
ven di rumeners zenen gekumen nokh a mol tsurik, zenen tsurikgekumen tsun undz, bay di daytshn shoyn, dos iz geven in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:05:51.096 --> 00:05:53.064
iz di rusn zaynen arayn,

00:05:52.935 --> 00:05:54.191
di r- di r-

00:05:53.256 --> 00:05:54.397
gedenkt ir?

00:05:54.191 --> 00:06:03.509
di rusn zenen arayngekumen, zenen opgeven a yor tsayt, un nokh dem zenen zey avekgegangen fun undz, un s'hot tsurikgenemen di rumenyens mit di daytshns. dos hot zikh ongehoybn di velts-milkhome.

00:06:05.743 --> 00:06:07.036
iz geven

00:06:07.617 --> 00:06:08.761
krigeray

00:06:08.761 --> 00:06:09.889
arum aykh?

00:06:10.485 --> 00:06:12.099
iz geven shiseray?

00:06:12.038 --> 00:06:13.736
s'i- vos heyst nit geven?

00:06:12.308 --> 00:06:13.466
armey?

00:06:13.742 --> 00:06:16.419
vos, vos hot ir gezen? dertseylt.

00:06:17.488 --> 00:06:19.780
 di r- di ershte,

00:06:19.780 --> 00:06:21.887
⟨a⟩ SNARYAD iz gefaln bay undz,

00:06:22.602 --> 00:06:24.604
 donershtik in shtot.

00:06:25.858 --> 00:06:28.113
in velkhn tog, velkhe date?

00:06:26.025 --> 00:06:26.876
UNK

00:06:27.968 --> 00:06:31.016
velkhe date? date kon ikh nit gedenken.

00:06:31.039 --> 00:06:36.517
iz, ale yidn zenen shoyn gegangen zikh bahaltn. ver s'hot zikh gebahaltn in a keler, ver s'hot zikh gebahaltn.

00:06:36.540 --> 00:06:39.554
un fraytik iz shoyn arayngekumen di,

00:06:39.898 --> 00:06:41.782
di rumener mit di daytshn.

00:06:42.463 --> 00:06:44.971
⟨i⟩n dem zelbn tog vos zey zenen arayngekumen,

00:06:44.995 --> 00:06:46.963
hot men teykef geshosn yidn.

00:06:48.167 --> 00:06:50.355
 vos hot pasirt? vos hot ir gezen?

00:06:51.205 --> 00:06:52.667
vos hot pasirt?

00:06:53.196 --> 00:06:58.337
ikh hob gezen ven zey zenen gegangen mit di biksn un ⟨m'iz⟩ arayngegan in a, in a shtub arayn,

00:06:58.461 --> 00:07:02.049
lebn undz, un m'hot geshosn a, a altn mentshn.

00:07:03.490 --> 00:07:09.879
un nokh dem hot men undz farnemen... in, in finef-zeks teg hot men undz farn-, arayngenemen in a, in a shul,

00:07:10.560 --> 00:07:15.448
un, s'iz geshtanen di rumener mit di daytshn, un s'iz geven di poyers,

00:07:16.703 --> 00:07:18.907
di vos zey hobn gevoynt in dem shtetl,

00:07:19.048 --> 00:07:22.586
un m'hot genemen dos, di mener bazunder

00:07:22.677 --> 00:07:24.476
un di froyen bazunder.

00:07:25.039 --> 00:07:32.508
un, un m'hot ersht opge- dos hot ⟨men undz⟩ gehaltn tsvey teg dortn, un nokh dem hot men undz opgelozt, di froyen mit di kinder hot men opgelozt,

00:07:32.565 --> 00:07:35.613
un mener, eltere mentshn, hot men oykhet opgelozt.

00:07:35.653 --> 00:07:36.541
⟨ven⟩

00:07:35.653 --> 00:07:37.868
un yunge, yunge khevre,

00:07:37.868 --> 00:07:39.781
epes hundert draysik mentshn,

00:07:40.463 --> 00:07:43.461
hot men, genemen un m'hot zey oysgeshosn teykef.

00:07:43.602 --> 00:07:46.475
hundert draysik mentshn, yunge khevre un,

00:07:46.475 --> 00:07:49.361
un vos m'hot gezogt az der iz geven a,

00:07:50.588 --> 00:07:52.792
a komunist, ver s'iz geven,....

00:07:53.608 --> 00:07:56.538
ven s'iz arayngekumen di rusishe, zey hobn gearbet baym rusishn,

00:07:56.747 --> 00:08:00.347
hobn zey shoyn geshikt, hobn zey gerekhnt az dos iz shoyn

00:08:00.578 --> 00:08:02.965
andere PART⟨II⟩.

00:08:03.582 --> 00:08:06.394
iz hundert draysik mentshn hot men teykef oysgeshosn.

00:08:06.754 --> 00:08:07.625
un nokh...

00:08:06.771 --> 00:08:07.510
mit,

00:08:07.510 --> 00:08:09.262
mit vemen zayt ir geven

00:08:09.319 --> 00:08:10.480
in di teg,

00:08:10.480 --> 00:08:13.178
ven di rumener un di daytshn zaynen arayn?

00:08:12.424 --> 00:08:13.785
mit di eltern!

00:08:14.162 --> 00:08:16.597
un ayere brider un shvester?

00:08:15.850 --> 00:08:17.361
yo. yo.

00:08:16.597 --> 00:08:18.611
ale tsuzamen in eynem?

00:08:18.162 --> 00:08:19.084
yo.

00:08:21.300 --> 00:08:26.879
vos hot, vos gedenkt ir fun... vos hot men gezogt? vos hot ayer, ayer tate-mame gezogt?

00:08:27.021 --> 00:08:29.791
zey hobn aykh baruikt mit epes?

00:08:27.582 --> 00:08:28.582
⟨ah⟩

00:08:29.791 --> 00:08:30.946
mit verter?

00:08:30.835 --> 00:08:33.270
mir hob'mir moyre gehat, UNK ⟨mir, mir zenen⟩ gezesn in shtub,

00:08:33.270 --> 00:08:35.626
un teykef, un azoy vi

00:08:35.863 --> 00:08:38.914
s'iz arayngekumen di rumener mit di daytshn,

00:08:38.914 --> 00:08:43.029
iz teykef, di poyers zenen gekumen un hobn bay undz aldings aroysgenemen fun der shtub.

00:08:43.474 --> 00:08:45.527
un mir hobn mir nit getort zogn gornit.

00:08:46.090 --> 00:08:50.657
un ven m'hot undz aroysgetribn in der shil aray- in der shul arayn, di shkole dortn,

00:08:50.832 --> 00:08:55.264
un zenen mir tsurikgekumen, hobn mir shoyn nit getrofn gornit in shtub. der fentster iz shoyn geven tsebrokhn.

00:08:55.540 --> 00:08:59.027
vos s'iz geven hobn zey shoyn oy-, tsugen-... s'iz geven vi a p⟨ro⟩grom!

00:09:01.311 --> 00:09:03.094
in a vokh arum

00:09:03.977 --> 00:09:07.396
nokh dem, hot men undz aroysgetribn fun, VOOBSHCHE ale yidn,

00:09:07.673 --> 00:09:09.489
fun de- fun dem shtetl.

00:09:10.086 --> 00:09:11.750
zenen mir gegan tsu fus.

00:09:12.145 --> 00:09:14.299
hot men undz getribn tsu fus.

00:09:14.338 --> 00:09:17.943
un s'iz geven shtark groyse hitsn. mentshn zenen gefaln oyfn veg;

00:09:18.490 --> 00:09:21.001
eltern, vos zey hobn shoyn nit gekont geyn,

00:09:21.001 --> 00:09:25.318
hobn gedarft iberlozn di... di kinder hobn gedarft iberlozn di eltern,

00:09:25.881 --> 00:09:28.966
vayl zey hobn gevolt oyfheybn di eltern, hot men nit gelozt.

00:09:28.966 --> 00:09:30.600
hobn zey ge- shtark geshlogn.

00:09:30.775 --> 00:09:34.633
iz ⟨m- iz⟩ hot men ibergelozt di eltern. kinder hot men ibergelozt azoy oyfn veg.

00:09:34.302 --> 00:09:35.815
ver hot aykh getribn?

00:09:35.888 --> 00:09:37.333
⟨di⟩ UNK...

00:09:36.259 --> 00:09:37.417
daytshn

00:09:37.474 --> 00:09:38.929
s'hot undz getribn

00:09:37.592 --> 00:09:39.324
tsi, rumener?

00:09:38.929 --> 00:09:39.796
rumener.

00:09:40.123 --> 00:09:42.513
zey zaynen geven oyf ferd, tsi

00:09:41.963 --> 00:09:42.986
neyn.

00:09:42.891 --> 00:09:44.387
oyf vogn un...?

00:09:45.321 --> 00:09:48.504
vos far a... mashinen? zey hobn gehat mashinen?

00:09:47.413 --> 00:09:50.832
⟨n-⟩ zey hobn nit gehat keyn... vos zhe, in Rumenye iz geven mashinen? oyf ferd!

00:09:50.063 --> 00:09:52.487
⟨ah, zey zaynen⟩ geganen, geganen tsu fus oykh?

00:09:51.413 --> 00:09:55.288
oyf ferd. ⟨iz men⟩ gegan tsu fus un m'hot undz getribn vi shof.

00:09:56.087 --> 00:09:58.308
⟨s'heyst⟩ zey hobn yo gehat ferd oykh?

00:09:57.505 --> 00:09:58.674
yo, yo.

00:09:58.674 --> 00:10:01.666
etlekhe hobn gehat ferd, un s'iberike iz gegan tsu fus.

00:10:02.027 --> 00:10:06.729
s'hot undz gefirt mistome, ah... a- azoy fil mentshn, hot undz gefirt mistome a tsen soldatn.

00:10:07.866 --> 00:10:10.577
un mir ze'mir gegan ale; m'hot moyre gehat az...

00:10:10.313 --> 00:10:12.855
vifl mentshn zayt ir geven oyfn veg?

00:10:13.300 --> 00:10:14.694
oyfn veg?

00:10:13.367 --> 00:10:15.031
vifl rekhnt ir?

00:10:15.426 --> 00:10:18.609
 dos UNK geven a akht-nayn toyznt mentshn.

00:10:19.830 --> 00:10:21.579
ale fun der shtot?

00:10:20.910 --> 00:10:28.362
fun der shtot, fun di, ale yidn hot men aroysgetribn. m'hot dokh keyner nit gevust tsi s'⟨vet⟩ di, s'⟨vet⟩ araynkumen di rumener, az... dos iz ge- forgekumen in eyn tog.

00:10:29.702 --> 00:10:35.568
 di nit-yidishe shkheynim, hot ir ⟨ge-⟩ zey gezen tsvishn di, di rumener un daytshn? zey hobn

00:10:35.575 --> 00:10:37.459
onteyl genumen ⟨bay⟩...?

00:10:36.570 --> 00:10:39.180
neyn! neyn, neyn, neyn.

00:10:39.979 --> 00:10:42.453
ver kon nemen a aynteyl in derin? keyner nit!

00:10:43.489 --> 00:10:47.654
iz, zey vos hobn aykh, getribn un ze- zey vos hobn geshosn

00:10:47.654 --> 00:10:50.536
yidn dort zaynen geven nor, soldatn?

00:10:49.851 --> 00:10:51.138
nor soldatn.

00:10:52.872 --> 00:10:56.966
vos hobn di... ir hot geredt mit, shkheynim v- nit-yidishe

00:10:57.867 --> 00:10:59.585
ven zenen mir gegangen?

00:10:58.018 --> 00:10:59.649
in der tsayt? yo.

00:10:59.585 --> 00:11:00.143
yo.

00:10:59.993 --> 00:11:01.421
vos hobn zey gezogt?

00:11:00.143 --> 00:11:01.421
UNK geven UNK...

00:11:01.613 --> 00:11:04.847
