 mikh hot ⟨men⟩ nit genemen, nor m'hot genemen di eltere.

00:22:21.760 --> 00:22:24.999
m'hot zey genemen oyf arbet dortn, he....

00:22:26.232 --> 00:22:28.301
vos hobn ayer tate-mame geton?

