00:22:37.217 --> 00:22:39.686
neyn, ikh bin geven tsu yung; ikh bin geven a kind, ⟨⟩.

00:22:39.686 --> 00:22:43.930
ikh fleg mikh ontun vi a, a poyershe ontun zikh

00:22:43.930 --> 00:22:47.049
un ikh fleg aray- aroysgeyn fun der geto. ikh fleg aroysgeyn.

