kh'fleg geyn, fleg ikh betn bay di poyerim. flegn mir gibn broyt un flegn mir gibn kartoflyes. me fleg mir gibn a shtikl kez, vos nit iz.

00:22:54.863 --> 00:22:58.780
azoy fleg ikh mikh tsurik araynganvenen in geto un me fleg brengen dos esn.

00:22:58.780 --> 00:23:02.372
iz ale mentshn vos, iz geven gern, ⟨er⟩ zol khapn a sh⟨tikl⟩ broyt,

00:23:03.222 --> 00:23:07.806
me zol zey gibn a bisl broyt. ikh hob f- ikh hob mikh ongetun vi zey- zeyere kinder.

00:23:07.812 --> 00:23:11.802
m'hot mir gemakht a lange yupke, mit a tikhl farbunen,

00:23:11.802 --> 00:23:13.746
iz di daytsh hot mikh nit derkent.

00:23:14.612 --> 00:23:19.027
dos fleg ikh aroysloyfn un betn bay zey, un zey flegn gibn. zey flegn gibn.

00:23:20.923 --> 00:23:24.494
un di poyerim hobn gevust az ir zayt a bahaltener yid?

00:23:24.130 --> 00:23:27.246
yo. yo, yo. zey hobn gevust, di poyerim.

00:23:24.568 --> 00:23:25.541
yidene...

00:23:25.817 --> 00:23:27.195
yidishe...

00:23:29.378 --> 00:23:30.756
iz,

00:23:31.943 --> 00:23:33.877
vos far a sekone iz geven

00:23:33.900 --> 00:23:35.446
tsu ant- tsu

00:23:35.790 --> 00:23:37.356
antloyfn fun geto,

00:23:37.356 --> 00:23:39.581
tsu, aroysganvenen fun geto?

00:23:39.823 --> 00:23:43.715
⟨ah, n⟩⟨UNK⟩ m'hot gedarft durkhgeyn durkh di soldatn.

00:23:44.920 --> 00:23:47.057
arum un arum iz geshtanen soldatn;

00:23:47.367 --> 00:23:48.790
m'hot gedarft durkhgeyn.

00:23:48.790 --> 00:23:50.477
nor zey hobn mikh nit derkent,

00:23:50.477 --> 00:23:55.292
az ikh bin a yidishke. ikh bin geven farbunen, azoy vi se geyen zeyer, di poyer⟨im'⟩s kinder.

00:23:55.382 --> 00:24:00.202
geven a kind., nu, a kind hobn zey azoy nit gekukt oyf mir, me, fleg ikh a- aroysgeyn zikh.

00:24:01.440 --> 00:24:06.463
vi azoy i- iz geven meglekh aroystsuganvenen fun geto? iz geven...

00:24:06.705 --> 00:24:10.124
vu azoy, vi azoy, gedenkt ir, ir zayt aroys fun geto?

00:24:09.793 --> 00:24:13.432
nu, ikh bin gegangen., der poyer iz gesht- der soldat iz geshtanen.

00:24:13.675 --> 00:24:16.774
ah, ir zayt, gl-, glat farbaygegangen?

00:24:15.953 --> 00:24:16.875
yo.

00:24:16.999 --> 00:24:21.060
bin aroysgegangen, hot er gemeynt, ikh bin a poyershe, nit keyn yid, yid⟨in⟩.

00:24:21.437 --> 00:24:25.768
ir farshteyt?, hot er getrakht, ", s'iz dokh, a kind. zi geyt durkh."

00:24:26.314 --> 00:24:28.569
er hot mikh nit derkent az ikh bin a yidishke.

00:24:29.470 --> 00:24:31.725
iz durkhn soldat fleg ikh durkhgeyn.

00:24:32.997 --> 00:24:34.155
un

00:24:34.212 --> 00:24:37.378
far vos hot ir nisht moyre gehat az di poyerim veln

00:24:38.076 --> 00:24:40.685
aykh, ibergebn tsu di daytshn?

00:24:40.253 --> 00:24:41.158
neyn.

00:24:41.923 --> 00:24:43.793
zey fl- zey hobn dos nit geton.

00:24:43.793 --> 00:24:46.237
keyns nit. zey flegn nokh bahaltn di yidn.

00:24:50.698 --> 00:24:53.190
⟨ven⟩ zey hobn gezen az ikh bin a kind, az ikh gey,

00:24:53.190 --> 00:24:57.749
ikh bin gegan azoy fil mayl; es iz dokh nit geven do teykef. ikh bin gegan mistome a tsen mayl tsu fus.

00:24:57.749 --> 00:24:59.063
a kleyn kind!

00:25:00.233 --> 00:25:07.224
un ikh bin arayngekumen in dem, sht-, derfl arayn, ⟨vi azoy me zogt⟩, bay di kristn, dortn nit geven keyn yidn,

00:25:07.224 --> 00:25:10.976
iz, yeder hot mir gegibn esn. m'hot mir gegibn, m'hot mikh ongehodevet.

00:25:16.180 --> 00:25:22.974
un azoy fleg ikh geyn betn un ikh fleg hodeven di, mayn, mame un mayn tatn. zey hot men nit aroysgelozt;

00:25:22.997 --> 00:25:24.746
s'iz geven eltere mentshn.

00:25:26.220 --> 00:25:31.212
un nokh dem hobn zey tsugenemen, mayn, bruder un mayn tatn hot men avekgenemen,

00:25:31.212 --> 00:25:33.605
di daytshn, keyn Vapnyarke

00:25:34.776 --> 00:25:36.090
oyf arbet.

00:25:35.518 --> 00:25:36.592
vu iz dos?

00:25:36.909 --> 00:25:38.212
V⟨a⟩pnyarke.

00:25:38.455 --> 00:25:39.714
