00:25:45.981 --> 00:25:47.814
bay di,

00:25:51.415 --> 00:25:54.806
bay vos hobn zey gearbet dortn? ikh gedenk nit bay vos zey hobn gearbet.

00:25:54.806 --> 00:25:56.724
un in fir khadoshim arum

00:25:57.203 --> 00:25:59.239
iz, zenen zey aheymgekumen.

