00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:10.725
ver iz u- ver iz umgekumen?

00:26:10.725 --> 00:26:11.903
ay-

00:26:10.737 --> 00:26:13.178
mayn, tate mit mayn, bruder.

00:26:13.639 --> 00:26:17.632
zey hobn genemen, nit in dem shtetl; zey hobn zey avekgefirt vayt.

00:26:19.174 --> 00:26:21.497
nit nor zey; m'hot genemen a sakh mentshn.

00:26:22.600 --> 00:26:26.711
m'iz arayngekumen in geto ⟨un⟩ vemen m'hot gevolt, dem hot men genemen.

00:26:25.722 --> 00:26:27.943
ir, ir hot nisht gehert fun zey?

00:26:28.118 --> 00:26:29.074
fun vemen?

00:26:28.911 --> 00:26:31.065
fun ayer tate un ayer bruder?

00:26:30.683 --> 00:26:34.896
neyn. un nokh dem in fir, khadoshim arum zenen zey aheymge- tsurikgekumen.

00:26:38.293 --> 00:26:40.003
oh, zey zaynen tsurikgekumen.

00:26:39.768 --> 00:26:40.768
yo.

00:26:40.003 --> 00:26:41.240
iz,

00:26:41.533 --> 00:26:43.889
vos hobn dey d- zey dertseylt

00:26:44.976 --> 00:26:46.539
vegn,...?

00:26:45.617 --> 00:26:48.319
oy, shtark shlekht vos hot men dertseylt dortn.

00:26:48.351 --> 00:26:50.403
a gantsn tog hot men gearbet.

00:26:51.253 --> 00:26:53.609
nu, pravde, m'hot zey dortn gegibn esn.

00:26:53.852 --> 00:26:55.736
m'hot zey gegibn esn dortn.

00:26:56.046 --> 00:26:59.482
un, un a sakh mentshn hot men oysgeharget.

00:27:03.943 --> 00:27:06.367
zey zaynen g- tsurikgekumen gezunt?

